	   <tr><td colspan=2>as a barb shaman on a pvp server i would think this belt would be awesome. as some people know all large races get slam, though its not a levelable skill it still gives a chance of a spell interupt or a stun. in pvp every stun is one less hit you take and every interupt is another spell that doesnt land. with a shaman haste buff and this item i would gladly take on a melee any day. with all the buffs available to shaman plus the great weapons out there plus a fairly good amount of weapon skill, we are a force to be reckoned with. at lvl 47 i have 1400hps 1000ac 157str 149 sta 150agl 101dex and still have 171wis with only my own buffs. my attack is around 700 which isnt great but if i dont have the agro its more than sufficient. and beleive it or not a wis caster can and does proc weapons very often. i can average one proc per 4 rounds, sometimes less sometimes more. there is nothing i find more fun than actually beating a melee at his/her own game=)<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
